Marguerite Moreau https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marguerite_Moreau 0 Marguerite C. Moreau (born April 25, 1977) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Jesse Reeves in the fantasy horror film Queen of the Damned, Katie in the comedy Wet Hot American Summer, and her role in The Mighty Ducks series of films. She has also made appearances on the popular television series Smallville, Lost, Cupid and The O.C. Marguerite_C._Moreau ( born April_25_,_1977 ) is an_American_actress .
